snippet.title: Outcast 2 - A New Beginning | Legend of the Ulukaï (Part 1)
snippet.description:
They called him renegade, traitor, an outcast on two planets. Listen to Maar telling you the Legend of the Ulukaï for Outcast 2: A New Beginning. 

Outcast 2 - A New Beginning is coming to PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S.
